        {
            "title": "伊朗總統表示將停止對鄰國的攻擊",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"410\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/lLdBaG87BBpyRsw_qunzPQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNg--/https://i-invdn-com.investing.com/news/STOCK-EXCHANGE-RUSSIAN-TRADING-SYSTEMS_M_1440048891.jpg\" width=\"650\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><strong>Investing.com</strong> — 伊朗總統馬蘇德·佩澤什基安週六宣布,德黑蘭領導層已批准暫停進攻性導彈襲擊,這可能緩和已經擾亂全球能源市場的地區衝突。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">該指令由臨時領導委員會批准,規定伊朗將停止對鄰國的攻擊,前提是沒有針對伊斯蘭共和國的襲擊從這些國家的領土發起。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">這項「不首先發動攻擊」政策標誌著德黑蘭的重大轉變,自2月份局勢升級以來,伊朗一直與美國和以色列軍隊處於直接軍事對抗狀態。該地區一週以來一直處於一觸即發的緊張狀態,伊斯蘭革命衛隊對鄰國發動了多次攻擊。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-2c87685f-e21a-34ee-95e1-d32562164579-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">佩澤什基安的聲明似乎旨在向地區鄰國,特別是那些駐有美軍基地的國家發出信號,如果它們保持中立,就不會成為攻擊目標。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">這場戰爭已經嚴重破壞了伊朗的國內基礎設施,此舉可能是為了獲得必要的「喘息空間」,以修復重要的能源設施,並應對持續的「石油衝擊」所引發的國內經濟不滿情緒。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><em>此文章由人工智能協助翻譯。更多資訊，請參閱我們的使用條款。</em></p></div>",
